    "body": "## Purpose\n\nCreative/product foundation for Stage 6 Step 9 before Codex implementation.\n\nThis PR remains deliberately **draft** and **documentation/data only**. It does not modify runtime/game code and is not frozen implementation authority.\n\n## Authority\n\nBaseline current main: `7673f3487b0dd52c0c5cb2c7826f4e3fe5cc570e`.\n\nTarget profiles: `RU_BOOMER / RU_GEN_X / RU_MILLENNIAL / RU_ZOOMER / RU_ALPHA`.\n\nRule: `NO FALSE OR MISUSED SLANG`, not `NO SLANG`. Russian cultural lanes must not be produced by translating or mixing foreign generational culture.\n\n## Completed foundation steps\n\n### ✅ 1. FULL_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE\n\nExecuted as a complete current-foundation rewrite overlay:\n\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE_V1.md`\n- `stage6_step9_alpha_ru_rewrite_v1.json`\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_CORRECTION.md`\n\nAlpha is now Russian-first at I0/I1, with selective authentic W/L, NPC, cooked, mid, skill issue, репорт, ивент, КД and similar markers only where semantically correct.\n\n### ✅ 2. RU_CULTURAL_AUTHENTICITY_PASS B/X/M/Z/A\n\nCompleted as a draft review pass:\n\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_RU_CULTURAL_AUTHENTICITY_PASS_V1.md`\n\nThe pass reviewed Batch 1-4, onboarding, NPC pools and the Alpha overlay across all five Russian-speaking cultural lanes.\n\nKey corrections include:\n\n- Boomer officialese/bureaucratic caricature reduced;\n- generic Gen X UI separated from 90s gangster cosplay, while literal bandit/mafia roles may keep role-authentic street register;\n- Millennial corporate-calque patterns replaced with more natural Russian RuNet-era voice;\n- Zoomer translated/imported phrasing reduced where it was not natural Russian-speaking usage;\n- Alpha calques/over-English patterns further corrected;\n- accessibility stepper labels explicitly classified as intentionally shared clear Russian.\n\nStep 2 is complete **as a creative draft review pass**, not frozen/approved implementation copy.\n\n## Resolved blocked source/product decisions\n\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_SOURCE_DECISIONS_RESOLVED.md`\n\n`npcArrest*`:\n\n- classified `LEGACY_ORPHAN_COPY / LEGACY_SUPERSEDED_CANDIDATE`;\n- removed from the generational creative queue;\n- deletion remains deferred until fresh inventory/gap closure proves no hidden dependency.\n\nDisabled P2P block:\n\n- product decision: `HIDE_DISABLED_P2P_BLOCK_UNTIL_FEATURE_ENABLED`;\n- do not generationally rewrite `P2P: анти-абуз.`;\n- do not show the unfinished `Недоступно. / P2P: анти-абуз. / Почему?` block while P2P capability is off.\n\n## Step 3 started: fresh current-main inventory\n\n- `STAGE6_STEP9_FRESH_CURRENT_MAIN_INVENTORY_PREFLIGHT.md`\n\nThe supplied `FULL_TEXT_INVENTORY_CURRENT_MAIN_PACKAGE.zip` is confirmed historical seed only:\n\n- seed commit: `e94e4bcb888f4a1e54b2879e3a810118e53a62d9`;\n- current main: `7673f3487b0dd52c0c5cb2c7826f4e3fe5cc570e`.\n\nExact blob audit proves:\n\n- `npcs.js` and `ui-menu.js` match the seed blob and may be reused only as static extraction candidates;\n- `data.js`, `system.js`, `ui-dm.js`, `ui-events.js`, `ui-battles.js` changed and require fresh extraction;\n- seed fallback rows for `index.html`, `state.js`, `ui-boot.js`, `ui-core.js` lacked deterministic source blob identity and require fresh re-extraction;\n- current routed source scope extends beyond the old 11-file seed list, including `events.js`, `conflict/conflict-core.js`, late presentation routing and post-PR258 paths.\n\nNo fake fresh total has been manufactured from stale counts.\n\n## Structural findings retained\n\n- Gen X partial plumbing exists but is not first-class.\n- Historical seed core: `Zoomer == Alpha` on `57/57` resolved keys; `Boomer == Millennial` on `19/57`.\n- Historical seed: 1930 active records / 853 unique texts / 306 dynamic templates. These numbers are not current-main authority.\n- PR #258 unified stat-toast architecture must remain.\n\n## Status\n\n`STAGE 6: NOT COMPLETE`\n\n`STEP 9: FOUNDATION_IN_PROGRESS / NOT_FROZEN`\n\nChecklist:\n- [x] 1. FULL_ALPHA_RUSSIAN_FIRST_REWRITE\n- [x] 2. RU_CULTURAL_AUTHENTICITY_PASS B/X/M/Z/A\n- [ ] 3. FRESH_CURRENT_MAIN_INVENTORY - preflight complete, deterministic rebuild in progress\n- [ ] 4. GAP_CLOSURE\n- [ ] 5. USER_REVIEW\n- [ ] 6. FREEZE + SHA256\n- [ ] 7. CODEX_IMPLEMENTATION\n\nNext action: `FRESH_CURRENT_MAIN_INVENTORY_DETERMINISTIC_REBUILD`.",
